The Soviet Union was really  

268
00:24:31,040 --> 00:24:37,200
dependent on oil exports, still is.
Oil prices tanked and oil accounted  

269
00:24:37,200 --> 00:24:42,960
for up to 55% of the Soviet budget.
So here Brezhnev has got a deep bench  

270
00:24:42,960 --> 00:24:49,120
of non-performing piles at a time when he 
doesn't have the money to support all of them. 

271
00:24:49,120 --> 00:24:54,240
Worse yet from the Soviet point of view, 
it's dumped all this money in these Third  

272
00:24:54,240 --> 00:25:00,240
World friends but meanwhile, it's got its 
