273
00:25:00,240 --> 00:25:04,720
and they want out of the empire.
Most problematically, they all  

274
00:25:04,720 --> 00:25:08,080
revolt at exactly the same time.
One of the rules for continental  

275
00:25:08,080 --> 00:25:12,480
empire is "no two-front wars".
Russia has so many fronts at  

276
00:25:12,480 --> 00:25:18,960
this point, it can't even keep count.
The unrest in the internal empire of  

277
00:25:18,960 --> 00:25:24,320
nationalities started as soon as Gorbachev got in.
There were student movements in Kazakhstan and  

278
00:25:24,320 --> 00:25:28,800
Yakutia, opposite ends of things.
By the time you get to 1990,  

279
00:25:28,800 --> 00:25:34,480
there are like 76 seething ethnic 
rebellions in different parts of this. 

280
00:25:34,480 --> 00:25:38,560
There was too much going on for 
the Soviet government to handle. 

281
00:25:38,560 --> 00:25:44,000
So you could argue that the Soviet Union 
bankrupted itself with the Third World while  

282
00:25:44,800 --> 00:25:48,800
ignoring its own internal Third World 
