283
00:25:48,800 --> 00:27:07,600
revolts brought down the Soviet Union.
I got a completely different argument for you. 

284
00:27:07,600 --> 00:27:11,120
If you don't like all of those, I got 
another one for you. It's the economy,  

285
00:27:11,120 --> 00:27:18,720
stupid, right? That line. One could argue 
